  "title": "Rebar/ System Formwork Supervisor |MainCon | Construction Industry",
  "description": "<p>Our client is a well-established A1 contracting firm with General Building and Civil Engineering projects.</p><p>CW01 General Building |CW02 Civil Engineering | GB1 General Builder Class 1 | Maincon Company</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><ul><li>Assembles and Dismantles system formwork (wall slabs, ceilings, etc) for complex and critical works</li><li>Lead, communicate and guide a team of 6 - 8 fresh workers with little to no formwork experience</li><li>Support co-workers to execute the project requirements</li><li>Plan and organise work to meet expected outcomes as arranged by Project Managers, Constrcution Managers and Foremen</li><li>Work in accordance with the personal health, safety and environment protocols at construction sites</li><li>Ensure a safe work place for all</li><li>Ad-hoc tasks as arranged by supervisors</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>At least 3-5 years of formwork/ rebar supervisor experience</li><li>Valid Work-At-Height and BCSS certs</li><li>Valid Supervise Formwork Cert preferred</li><li>Able to work 6 days per week, Mon - Saturday 8AM - 5PM, OT Rate shall be paid as per the Employment Act at 1.5x. Sunday 2.0x</li><li>Valid SEC(k) cert - enhanced formwork preferred</li></ul><p>We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. By submitting your application, you hereby give consent to Equator Search Pte Ltd (MOM Licence No 14C7203), for the collection, use and disclosure of the personal data in accordance with the Personal Data Protection Act (PDPA).</p><p><br /></p><p>Ready to take on the new role? WHATSAPP US AT +65 <a href=\"https://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapi.whatsapp.com%2Fsend%3Fphone%3D6568173075%26text%3DLink%253A%250Ahttps%253A%252F%252Ffb.me%252F8iG1RcbZN%250A%250AI%2520saw%2520this%2520on%2520Facebook...%26context%3DAfcY1EmiiGmwnVa_lkNI3XyCGTrve8RwfTupDh0Eg1QjhW6jCabvtjbqJes-jX33Jl139cLtLCVIFssUXyjgT5woMU90zJJyPhP37mnQz5opQPWgC2F